Package: fcc.gov
Title: FCC Open Data (Socrata SODA) Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the FCC Open Data Socrata SODA API. Covers
    dataset discovery, consumer complaints, broadband deployment, pirate radio
    enforcement, CSRIC best practices, 911 PSAP registry, equipment authorization,
    earth stations, and generic SoQL queries. Includes LLM context injection via
    fcc_context().
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    httr2,
    jsonlite,
    dplyr,
    tibble
